Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to regain the reputation of Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we must make the KC Grand Prix Duel Tournament we're holding this time a success no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone is plotting against me, but it's all pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll send them home with their tal between their legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, chosen Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jounouchi VS Mask the Rock"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an great atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s trying to tease them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, is he {\i1}that{\i0} stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OW!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Starting now, hosted by Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the most prestigious Duel Monsters Tournament, KC Grand Prix, will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The rules for this tournament are quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world's top level Duelists fighting in this tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will be divided among two categories, A and B, for the preliminary matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the one remaining will gain the glory of the KC Grand Prix winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, the one to win KC Grand Prix
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will be given the chance to fight the Battle City winner,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who holds the title of Duel King, Yugi Mutou, for a shot at his title!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, please take a look at the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're gonna announce the players of the tournament's first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First up is the A Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first challenger...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Katsuya Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awright! I'm up at the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The challenger...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mask The Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win the Duel, I get to take off that mask and reveal your true face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What "real face"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first match up in B Block will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leon Wilson VS Richard Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s also in the first round, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try your best, Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The pairing for the second match will be announced once the first match ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, please come up and greet everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner, I'll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yugi! Yugi! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can see you from down {\i0}there{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ladies and Gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just have one thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is neither a celebration nor a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a survival game with the Duelists betting their pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You will witness the loud cries of agony from many of the Duelists gathered here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and the victorious cry of but one from this group!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chosen Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, my Kaiba Land has become a Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you obtain glory or total defeat?\NIn order to survive, you must win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Show me just how determined you all are to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kaiba! Kaiba! Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...! In the end, he stole the spotlight for himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you, you rat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let you do whatever you want in this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the first round of the tournament will now commence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All matches will be held within the various stages within Kaiba Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only the winners from A and B may leave their selected stage victorious and return to this very arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first game in A Block will be held in the Amazon Cruise Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first game in B Block will be held in the Water Coaster area!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The participants may now move from the stage to the appointed locations!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give you any anesthesia in today's operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:08:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, think he's just someone identical to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, there's no mistaking him for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want some of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jounouchi! Why the hell are you {\i1}here{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna know {\i1}why{\i0}? Cuz I'm starved as hell and I need my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I gonna fight this on an empty stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IDIOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first game is about the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if you don't show up at the appointed location within 10 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're disqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:09:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT DID YOU SAY!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make it if we leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on the Amazon Cruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a {\i1}jungle{\i0}, and you only have {\i1}10{\i0} minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The right path appears to be that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Jounouchi!\N -Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! There's traps all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tell me sooner next time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Solid Vision, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we said it was Solid Vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much time left?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just 20 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four--!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You satisfied now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why are you here before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a path set aside just for staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}was{\i0} gonna guide you there, but you went and left before I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me earlier! Making us rush for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job making it here on time! I expect no less from my student!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I-I'm not your mentor or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're on about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi doesn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really noticed, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Hopkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him this definitely wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right! No one will know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arthur, I'm sick and tired of just staying home all the time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not so old that I'll lose to a bunch of youngsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Arthur, I got something else to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sugoroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why's he wearing that weird disguise? And it's totally obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, at least Jounouchi didn't discover him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he calls him his student?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will Sugoroku-{\i1}san{\i0} Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... My grandpa's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really {\i1}that{\i0} strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Your old man called us up and begged us to include him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he taught Yugi to Duel, so I thought it'd be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I've never seen your grandfather Duel before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, masked bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Swordsman of Landstar in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I set two cards. Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two cards on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Summon Wandering Mummy in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Little-Winguard in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I attack Wandering Mummy with Swordsman of Landstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Doesn't it have more Attack Points than yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Quick-Play Magic, Angel Dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can double my Monster's Attack Points based on the number I roll on the dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read right through that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Permanent Trap, Legendary Gambler!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card activates whenever the opponent uses dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my roll is higher than my opponents, I cancel out the effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the angel didn't work, let's have a match with the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Dice! It reduces the opponent's Attack depending on the number I roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Gambler is a Permanent Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I roll the die once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! I got six!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus the battle continues with their original Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have read entirely through you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:17:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Little-Winguard's Special Effect, at the End Phase, I can switch it to Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Jounouchi's mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Non Aggression Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card must be activated by discarding a card from your hand in the Standby Phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the opponent's next turn, their ability to Normal Summon and Special Summon is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also activate the Continuous Magic Card, Mirage of Nightmare, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, during the opponent's Standby Phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can draw from your deck until you hold four cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and during your Standby Phase, you are to discard the same number of cards at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is Grandpa Sugoroku's way of Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As expected. He's always two steps ahead of Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think that's all Grandpa is aiming for...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set a card and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Mirage of Nightmare's effects, I draw until I hold four cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I draw three cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on your turn, you have to discard the same number of cards in exchange, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open! Emergency Provisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card lets me send any number of Magic and Trap Cards on my field to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and recover my Life by 1000 for each in return!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the card I send to the Graveyard is... Mirage of Nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now when it is my turn, I don't have to discard any cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some cheap tricks you keep using!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the hell out of you for sure now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that Non Aggression Area is still in effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't Summon any Monsters this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's my turn. Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Field Magic from my hand, Metropolis of Ancient Times - Ancient City!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also sacrifice Wandering Mummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to Summon Ancient Giant in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if this card doesn't attack the opponent's Monster in a turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the player controlling this card suffers 300 points of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, what high Attack it has!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also the Continuous Magic from my hand! Ancient Key activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to this card's effect, I can Special Summon two Stone Giant Tokens in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the event these Stone Giant Tokens are not used to attack the opponent's Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the player will receive 500 points of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Ancient Giant to attack Little-Winguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:21:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll use the two Giant Stone Tokens to direct attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:22:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Sugoroku-{\i1}san{\i0}... No, I meant to say because of Mask the Rock's tactics,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi is greatly affected by him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of a mentor, he has Jounouchi completely read!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The impetuous Jounouchi is losing himself in the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! This isn't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to enjoy a Duel more!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Illusionary Ancient Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
